          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " the current context window \u2014 the messages, system prompt, tool results, and scratchpad text that are in scope for the current inference call. When the process ends or the context is cleared, short-term memory is gone."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Short-term memory is the LLM's primary working space. It holds:"
